Author: Majato
Title: [ANN][TOKEN SALE][BOUNTY] MAJATO – PROJECT FOR LEGAL CANNABIS INDUSTRY PRE-SALE!
Body: We are the Majato Project and we announce the Pre-Sale of MJT Tokens!   What is Majato: Majato is the revolutionary blockchain project in the legal cannabis industry with a double goal:   • create own legal cannabis production and distribution business in the State of California,   • create the blockchain-based Majato Platform that will unite the cannabis industry and utilize the Majato Token (MJT Token) as payment/settlement instrument within the Majato Platform.   The idea behind the Majato Project is to go farther than any other blockchain project in the legal cannabis industry. We want the Majato Platform to become the one-stop platform for all industry participants – from growers to labs to medical experts issuing medical cards to POS to consumers; the MJT Token to become the uniform payment instrument for cannabis products first in the U.S., then around the world; and launch our own legal cannabis production to ensure that each MJT Token owner will receive a certain quantity of the Project’s own cannabis for the Tokens, if that MJT Token owner decides to do so.   The Majato Mission:   • launch and evolve own production of cannabis in the U.S., beginning with indoor facilities in the State of California – a very real and tangible business with the purpose of backing the MJT Token with actual, tangible product in the form of produced cannabis;   • develop and deploy the one-stop, blockchain / smart contract-based Majato Platform that will provide long-sought transparency for the legal cannabis market through access to full product history in the seed-to-sale format, together with lab test results and seals of approval, and provide unique perks to each category of market participants – growers, labs, consumers, medical experts to name a few;   • introduce the ERC20 standard compliant MJT Token into the legal cannabis market as the uniform settlement instrument for the industry to finally resolve the problem with cashless payments for cannabis and grant MJT Token owners the ability to purchase cannabis for MJT Tokens in all locations and jurisdictions where the Project is launched;   • introduce and evolve the culture of “4C’s” – Conscious and Civilized Cannabis Consumption - through our educational and awareness activities and events, everywhere the Project is present.       Interested? Check out our official resources, join the pre-sale, get the tokens and help us grow! Above is just a brief summary of the project documents and we encourage you to read them!   The Majato Resources:   Official website: http://majato.io   FAQ: http://majato.io/faq   Presentation: http://majato.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Majato-Presentation.pdf   White Paper: http://majato.io/wpcontent/uploads/2017/11/Majato.White_.Paper_.V.2.3.ENG_.pdf       The Majato Team:   Our international team is comprised of US, German and Russian businessmen, lawyers and IT experts of high repute, and we are still adding experts to our advisory board. Check out the core team on our official website: https://majato.io!       The MJT Token Pre-sale:   When: MJT Token Pre-sale begins December 20, 2017 12:00 PM EST / 09:00 AM PST, ends on day all Tokens are purchased or on 45th day after start.   Soft cap: 800,000 MJT; if not reached – funds returned to Token buyers.   Overall Tokens for sale: 8,300,000 MJT Tokens offered for sale via crowd sale and private placement.   Price: 0,0022 ETH per MJT Token.   Bonuses: +10% to purchased Tokens if purchased on Pre-sale Week One (December 20 – December 26); +5% to purchased Tokens if purchased on Pre-sale Week Two (December 27 – January 2).  Private placement: If you want to purchase MJT Tokens for more than $10,000 (or equivalent), let us know – we are already accepting private placement requests and around 1/4 of the pre-sale MJT Tokens are already reserved.   Bounty: 700,000 MJT Tokens will be specifically reserved for those who want to lend the Project a helping hand with stuff like SMM, White Paper translations, community management etc.  Want to help us and get some bounty MJT Tokens, or have additional questions? Send your inquiries to info@majato.io and we will be happy to reply!

Title: [ANN][TOKEN SALE][BOUNTY] MAJATO – PROJECT FOR LEGAL CANNABIS INDUSTRY PRE-SALE!
Body: Hey CjMapope,  Thanks for the message. And here we were, playing fair and square. Whoa!  Yes, we do have a Wordpress site, thanks for pointing that out. Funny thing though, Microsoft, SAP, Techcrunch, Forbes and some others do the same. Do you know the reason? You better look at your site, which was launched just recently, and its design, oh, man. I mean, you need to be totally shit-faced AND retarded to come up with those “doodle faces” on that site. That ain’t no marijuana, son, that’s crack at work right there.   And yes, the literally virtual “network” you mention. What made you think we have none? Oh, sorry - you were not really asking - you were just trying to spill some beans before “the next round” of your presale stage. Right, more money from investors on some virtual bullshit which is as far from real marijuana business as you are far from Himalayas.   And, btw, here is another major difference between MJT and Perks, which you of course failed to mention. We are launching our own production so that each token will be backed by a certain amount of actual cannabis. PerksCoin – on the contrary - is not backed by anything real. As in, nada. Zilch. Nil. Jack shit. The only thing you provide is an intermediary network with a site of questionable quality.  So you better go and finally find some real industry businessmen to join your team, and at least redesign the symbol for your “PerksCoin” which blatantly and nearly completely copies the official Russian Ruble symbol. And once you do it, you better go and make your “cannabis user network” more secure and anonymous by throwing your login through Facebook and Instagram into trash  Nice try, asshole. Next time, try harder.
